These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-1::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, cabbage, carrot, garlic
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, chess, skydiving, writing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, epic, family, romance
City: hannover, miami, new-york, paris
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, japanese, pakistani, egyptian
 1. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1
 2. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the chinese##1
 3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1
 4. the japanese is on the right of the chinese##1
 5. the person traveling to hannover is the person eating asparagus##1
 6. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the chinese##1
 7. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
 8. the person eating carrot is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 9. the person watching family movies is the person eating asparagus##1
10. the pakistani is the person watching epic movies##1
11. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| Food          | cabbage    | carrot      | asparagus  | garlic     |
| Hobby         | writing    | skydiving   | card-games | chess      |
| Movie-Genre   | epic       | documentary | family     | romance    |
| City   | paris | miami         | hannover  | new-york    |
| Nationality           | pakistani      | egyptian       | chinese | japanese |

