.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, fanta, hot-chocolate
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, drama, satire, spy
There are 4 different favourite colors: red, lavender, apricot, azure
4 different pets are kept: ferret, hamster, pony, rat
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, august, june, july
 1. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 2. the person who likes red is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far right##1
 5. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
 7. the person who likes azure is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 8. the owner of the hamster is the person who likes azure##1
 9. the person watching satire movies is the person who likes apricot##1
10. the person who likes red is on the far right##1
11. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3     |       4       |
| Beverage      | coffee      | 7up     | fanta    | hot-chocolate |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | drama   | satire   | spy           |
| Color   | lavender  | azure     | apricot    | red         |
| Pet           | rat         | hamster | pony     | ferret        |
| Birthday         | december     | july  | august | june       |

