.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-3::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, cauliflower, grapes, lettuce
There are 4 different nationalities: american, british, chinese, french
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, satire, documentary, sports
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, camping, puzzles, collecting
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, subway, tram, trike
 1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
 3. the person eating grapes is the person watching sports movies##1
 4. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
 5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
 6. the person driving the trike is the person eating grapes##1
 7. the chinese is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
 8. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
 9. the french is the person watching satire movies##1
10. the british is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
11. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
12. the person eating grapes is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3    |       4       |
| Food          | cabbage    | lettuce      | grapes  | cauliflower   |
| Nationality   | french     | chinese      | british | american      |
| Movie-Genre           | satire       | adventure         | sports  | documentary         |
| Hobby         | skydiving | camping | puzzles  | collecting |
| Transport     | tram       | bike         | trike   | subway        |

