.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, soy-milk, sprite
4 different games are played: chess, go, billiard, whist
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, indonesian, japanese, thai
4 different pets are kept: cat, goat, guinea-pig, snake
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: dahlia, lily, daisy, bellflower
 1. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 2. the person playing whist is on the left of the person who growslily##1
 3. the person who growslily is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
 4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far right##1
 5. the person who growsdahlia is on the far left##1
 6. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
 7. the thai is on the far right##1
 8. the person playing whist is on the right of the japanese##1
 9. the indonesian is on the left of the person playing chess##1
10. the person drinking coffee is on the far right##1
11. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left##1
12. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person playing go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | soy-milk   | sprite   | cola      | coffee     |
| Game          | billiard     | chess   | whist | go |
| Nationality   | indonesian | japanese | chinese   | thai       |
| Pet           | goat       | cat      | snake     | guinea-pig |
| Flower     | dahlia    | daisy     | bellflower     | lily     |

