There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, emerald, blue, black
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, poppy, balloon-flower, orchid
 1. the dancer is the person who growsorchid##1
 2. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far left##1
 3. the person who likes emerald is on the far right##1
 4. the person who growspoppy is the person eating potato##1
 5. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person eating mango##1
 6. the musician is on the far right##1
 7. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 8. the person who growsorchid is the dancer##1
 9. the person eating pumpkin is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
10. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
11. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
12. the journalist is on the far left##1
13. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
14. the person who likes blue is on the right of the person who likes black##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3      |    4     |
