.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-6::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, dancing, gardening, skydiving
4 different games are played: bridge, billiard, mah-jongg, whist
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, daisy, orchid, daffodil
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cricket, rugby, snowboarding
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, car, ship, van
 1. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
 2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 4. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
 5. the person playing whist is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
 6. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 7. the person driving the ship is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 8. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
 9. the person who growsdaisy is on the far right##1
10. the person who's sport is rugby is the person driving the van##1
11. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person playing bridge##1
12. the person who growsorchid is the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |      4      |
| Hobby         | dancing   | gardening | skydiving    | card-games  |
| Game   | whist    | bridge | mah-jongg      | billiard |
| Flower   | orchid | tulip | daffodil         | daisy  |
| Sport         | climbing  | rugby     | snowboarding | cricket     |
| Transport     | bike      | van       | ship         | car         |

