 4. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 5. the person driving the van is on the far right##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far left##1
 7. the security-guard is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
 8. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the fisherman##1
 9. the person watching comedy movies is the person driving the subway##1
10. the person watching spy movies is the owner of the dog##1
11. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
12. the person watching musical movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |       2        |      3      |      4       |
| Movie-Genre    | comedy     | martial-arts  | spy       | musical      |
| Birthday       | july    | february        | october  | june      |
| Job         | fisherman  | security-guard | firefighter | photographer |
| Pet         | chinchilla | mouse          | dog         | hamster      |
| Transport   | subway     | helicopter     | trike       | van          |

