.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, mirinda, sprite, water
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, magic-tricks, video-games, woodworking
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, rowing, surfing, ice-hockey
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, helicopter, jet-ski, skateboard
4 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, rat, snake
 1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far left##1
 2. the person drinking mirinda is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 3. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 4. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
 5. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person drinking sprite##1
 6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person drinking water##1
 7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
 8. the person driving the bike is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
 9. the owner of the chinchilla is the person who's sport is surfing##1
10. the person who's sport is surfing is on the far left##1
11. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
12. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
