 7. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person eating lime##1
 8. the modern house is on the right of the person eating lime##1
 9. the person playing whist is on the right of the person eating plum##1
10. the modern house is the person eating raspberry##1
11. the cape-cod house is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
12. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far right##1
