.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-20::.
There 4 different types of food: apricot, asparagus, cherry, grapes
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, skydiving, sudoku, video-games
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, sports, action, fantasy
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, sprite, cola, iced-tea
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, scooter, ship, snowmobile
 1. the person watching fantasy movies is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 2. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
 3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
 5. the person drinking cola is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 6. the person eating cherry is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 7. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
 8. the person watching disaster movies is the person driving the motorbike##1
 9. the person eating cherry is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
10. the person eating grapes is the person drinking iced-tea##1
11. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
12. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person watching action movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |       3        |      4      |
| Food        | asparagus    | grapes        | apricot        | cherry      |
| Hobby       | sudoku       | fishing       | skydiving      | video-games |
| Movie-Genre         | sports | fantasy | action | disaster      |
| Beverage         | milk          | iced-tea         | sprite           | cola    |
| Transport   | ship         | scooter       | snowmobile     | motorbike   |

 